---
title: Resale Home Purchase Tracker
timezone: Asia/Kolkata
dateFormat: d/M/y

# Status colors (change a task's #tag to update its color)
#done: green
#active: blue
#blocked: red
#todo: gray
#milestone: purple
---

# Search & Shortlist

20/6/2026 - 3 weeks: Finalize budget & locality shortlist #done
  id: budget
  - [x] Decide max budget incl. registration + interiors
  - [x] Pick 2-3 target localities

after !budget 4 weeks: Site visits & shortlist property #active
  id: shortlist
  - [x] First round of visits
  - [ ] Second visits for top options
  - [ ] Lock final property

# Due Diligence
// These can only start once a property is shortlisted, so they hang off !shortlist

after !shortlist 2 weeks: Legal document verification #todo
  id: legal
  - [ ] Title deed & ownership chain
  - [ ] Encumbrance Certificate (13 years)
  - [ ] Approved building plan
  - [ ] Occupancy Certificate (OC)
  - [ ] Latest property tax receipts
  - [ ] Society NOC / share certificate

after !shortlist 1 week: Physical & technical inspection #todo
  id: inspection
  - [ ] Structural / seepage check
  - [ ] Verify carpet area vs documents

# Price & Agreement

!legal.end / 1 week: Negotiate price & pay token advance #todo
  id: token

after !token 1 week: Sign agreement to sell #milestone
  id: agreement

# Home Loan
// Pre-approval runs in parallel with due diligence; valuation waits for the agreement

after !shortlist 2 weeks: Loan pre-approval #todo
  id: preapproval

after !agreement 2 weeks: Bank legal & technical valuation #todo
  id: valuation

after !valuation 1 week: Loan sanction #milestone
  id: sanction

# Registration & Handover

!sanction.end / 2 weeks: Stamp duty payment & registration #todo
  id: registration

after !registration 3 days: Loan disbursement to seller #todo
  id: disbursement

after !disbursement 1 week: Possession & key handover #milestone
  id: handover

# Post-Possession

after !handover 2 weeks: Utility transfers (EB, water, gas) #todo
after !handover 3 weeks: Khata / property-tax name transfer #todo
after !handover 4 weeks: Society membership transfer #todo
